history.content:
Hello All,

I'm doing research on how EECS students interact with business students (and vice versa).

I'm interested in how these groups socialize and the perceptions between them. 

The aim is to increase collaboration on campus and to foster a culture of mutual respect, but I need your insights!

Anybody willing to chat for 10 minutes in person near campus either tonight or tomorrow between 11am and 2pm? Even if you've never met a business student, your insights are valuable. 

Thanks!

James
history.subject: EECS, Business, and Entrepreneurship
